  <entry>
    <title>Hello world!</title>
    <link href="http://naijoug.com/2016/01/01/Hello-world/"/>
    <id>http://naijoug.com/2016/01/01/Hello-world/</id>
    <published>2016-01-01T08:20:42.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-05-22T14:03:21.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>写一写，各种语言的“Hello world!”。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="Reference"><a href="#Reference" class="headerlink" title="Reference"></a>Reference</h2><ul><li><a href="https://learnxinyminutes.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">Learn X in Y minutes</a></li></ul><h2 id="C"><a href="#C" class="headerlink" title="C"></a>C</h2><figure class="highlight c"><figcaption><span>helloword.c</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> argc, <span class="keyword">char</span> *argv[])</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"Hello world!\n"</span>);</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ gcc helloworld.c          <span class="comment"># 编译&amp;链接.c文件</span></div><div class="line">$ ./a.out                   <span class="comment"># 运行可执行文件a.out</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="C-1"><a href="#C-1" class="headerlink" title="C++"></a>C++</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><figcaption><span>helloworld.cpp</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span><span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> <span class="built_in">std</span>;</div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> argc, <span class="keyword">char</span> *argv[])</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">"Hello world!\n"</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ g++ helloworld.cpp        <span class="comment"># 编译&amp;链接.cpp文件</span></div><div class="line">$ ./a.out                   <span class="comment"># 运行可执行文件a.out</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Objective-C"><a href="#Objective-C" class="headerlink" title="Objective-C"></a>Objective-C</h2><figure class="highlight objc"><figcaption><span>HelloWorld.m</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">#import <span class="meta-string">&lt;NSFoundation/NSFoundation.h&gt;</span></span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> main(<span class="keyword">int</span> argc, <span class="keyword">char</span> * argv[]) &#123; </div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">@autoreleasepool</span> &#123;</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">NSLog</span>(<span class="string">@"Hello world!"</span>);</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ gcc HelloWorld.m          <span class="comment"># 编译&amp;链接.m文件</span></div><div class="line">$ ./a.out                   <span class="comment"># 运行可执行文件a.out</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Swift"><a href="#Swift" class="headerlink" title="Swift"></a>Swift</h2><figure class="highlight swift"><figcaption><span>HelloWorld.swift</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> Foundation</div><div class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">"Hello world!"</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ swfitc HelloWorld.swift   <span class="comment"># 编译&amp;链接.swift文件</span></div><div class="line">$ ./HelloWorld              <span class="comment"># 运行可执行文件HelloWorld</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Java"><a href="#Java" class="headerlink" title="Java"></a>Java</h2><figure class="highlight java"><figcaption><span>HelloWorld.java</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">HelloWorld</span> </span>&#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123; </div><div class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">"Hello world!"</span>);</div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ javac Helloworld.java         <span class="comment"># 编译java文件(生成class文件)</span></div><div class="line">$ java Helloworld               <span class="comment"># 运行</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Go"><a href="#Go" class="headerlink" title="Go"></a>Go</h2><figure class="highlight go"><figcaption><span>helloworld.go</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="keyword">package</span> main</div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">"fmt"</span></div><div class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">func</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span> &#123;</div><div class="line">    fmt.Println(<span class="string">"Hello world!"</span>)</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ go run helloworld.go          <span class="comment"># 运行.go文件</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Python"><a href="#Python" class="headerlink" title="Python"></a>Python</h2><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>python2</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#!/usr/bin/python</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"Hello world!"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>python3</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#!/usr/bin/python3</span></div><div class="line">print(<span class="string">"Hello world!"</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ python helloworld.py          <span class="comment"># 运行.py文件</span></div><div class="line">$ python3 helloworld.py         <span class="comment"># 运行.py文件</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Ruby"><a href="#Ruby" class="headerlink" title="Ruby"></a>Ruby</h2><figure class="highlight ruby"><figcaption><span>helloworld.rb</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#!/usr/bin/ruby -w</span></div><div class="line">puts <span class="string">"Hello world!"</span>;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ ruby helloworld.rb            <span class="comment"># 运行.rb文件</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Perl"><a href="#Perl" class="headerlink" title="Perl"></a>Perl</h2><figure class="highlight perl"><figcaption><span>helloworld.pl</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment">#!/usr/bin/perl</span></div><div class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">"Helllo world!\n"</span>;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ chmod 755 helloworld.pl       <span class="comment"># 修改.pl文件权限</span></div><div class="line">$ ./helloworld.pl               <span class="comment"># 运行.pl文件</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;写一写，各种语言的“Hello world!”。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
